Attribute Name Tag Description Code Rule
Message ID Being Responded To 0000,0120 Shall be set to the value of the Message ID (0000,0110) field used in associated NEVENT-REPORT-RQ Message. IsRequiredRule / HasValueRule
Status (0000,0900) 000 for Success IsRequiredRule / ValueRule
Command Field 0000,0100 This field distinguishes the DIMSE-N operation conveyed by this Message. The value of this field shall be set to 8100H for the N-EVENT-REPORT-RSP Message. IsRequiredRule / ValueRule
Command Data Set Type 0000,0800 This field indicates if a Data Set is present in the Message. This field shall be set to the value of 0101H if no Data Set is present; any other value indicates a Data Set is included in the Message. IsRequiredRule / ValueRule
